      <title>激进分子埃利奥特增持英美资源集团价值 10 亿美元的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/activist-elliott-said-to-build-1-billion-anglo-american-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃利奥特投资管理公司(Elliott Investment Management)已持有英美资源集团(Anglo American Plc)约10亿美元的股份，同时做空必和必拓集团(BHP Group Ltd.)的股票，这家澳大利亚矿业公司主动收购了英美资源集团(Anglo American Plc)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/activist-elliott-said-to-build-1-billion-anglo-american-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 12:00:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国可能会阻碍必和必拓成为最大铜生产国的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/china-could-hinder-bhp-s-bid-to-become-copper-s-top-producer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团斥资 390 亿美元打造全球铜业巨头的举动可能会惹恼其最大客户中国，因为中国当局有干预阻止或淡化国际并购的历史。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/china-could-hinder-bhp-s-bid-to-become-copper-s-top-producer</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 07:32:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>必和必拓投标显示供应紧张，铜价触及每吨 10,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/copper-hits-10-000-a-ton-as-bulls-predict-looming-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铜价两年来首次触及每吨 10,000 美元，因为人们猜测全球矿山将难以满足即将到来的绿色工业浪潮的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/copper-hits-10-000-a-ton-as-bulls-predict-looming-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 06:04:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行维持关键利率不变，日元兑美元跌破157</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/yen-drops-to-fresh-34-year-low-as-boj-keeps-key-rate-unchanged</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行表示货币政策将保持宽松，日元兑美元汇率跌至 34 年来新低，并突破 157 的水平，加剧了当局可能很快干预市场以阻止日元贬值的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/yen-drops-to-fresh-34-year-low-as-boj-keeps-key-rate-unchanged</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 03:34:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
